Andrey wrote:
> 
> Also I tried using "Style <mytitle> NoHandles" which did not work...
> "Style <mytitle> NoTitle" left the border intact, even though it removed the
> title (as it should)...

The width of the border around windows is set in two ways:
1) "Style <mytitle> HandleWidth N" by default, and if "Style <mytitle>
Handles" is specified.
2) "Style <mytitle> BorderWidth N" if "Style <mytitle> NoHandles" is
used or the client indicates that it shouldn't be resized.

Try "Style <mytitle> HandleWidth 0" instead of ".. NoHandles".

Cheers,
Tim.


